data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern convenience. The roof, a vital component of any home, is a mere 3 years old, providing you with peace of mind and assurance in the durability of your investment. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a well-maintained oasis boasting high ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, equipped with sleek stainless steel appliances and an abundance of cabinets, offering both functionality and aesthetics for the culinary enthusiast. The primary bedroom is a spacious retreat, complete with an attached private bathroom and a walk-in closet, providing ample storage for your wardrobe. The additional bedrooms are equally generous in size, featuring window treatments that ensure both privacy and comfort for family members or guests. As you make your way through the living spaces, sliding glass doors beckon you to the screened-in lanai, perfect for enjoying the outdoors in a bug-free environment. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting gatherings in this delightful space. Venture into the large backyard, a rare find in many homes, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing under the open sky. This residence is not just a home; it's a haven for those who appreciate both indoor and outdoor living. Convenience is at your fingertips, with grocery stores just a stone's throw away, ensuring that your daily essentials are easily accessible. The proximity to State Road 60 adds another layer of convenience, providing swift access to nearby amenities and destinations. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained property your own. Embrace the comfort, charm, and practicality this home has to offer – schedule your viewing today and step into a future filled with cherished moments in this exceptional residence.
